  "_comment": [
    "╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗",
    "║           SKILLS.JSON — Catalogue centralisé des Skills            ║",
    "╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝",
    "",
    "Ce fichier est la source unique (single source of truth) pour toutes",
    "les skills affichées sur le dashboard et installées par connect_claude.",
    "",
    "AJOUTER UNE NOUVELLE SKILL :",
    "  1. Copier le modèle ci-dessous (template)",
    "  2. Le coller dans la section appropriée (defaults, packs, individual)",
    "  3. Remplir les champs, enregistrer → tout s'affiche automatiquement",
    "",
    "TEMPLATE SKILL INDIVIDUELLE :",
    "  {",
    "    \"id\": \"mon-skill-id\",",
    "    \"name\": \"Nom affiché sur le dashboard\",",
    "    \"description\": \"Description courte\",",
    "    \"icon\": \"🔧\",",
    "    \"repo\": \"github-user/repo-name\",",
    "    \"repo_url\": \"https://github.com/github-user/repo-name\",",
    "    \"author\": \"github-user\",",
    "    \"installs\": \"12.5K\",",
    "    \"tags\": [\"backend\", \"typescript\"],",
    "    \"agents\": [\"Claude Code\", \"Cursor\", \"GitHub Copilot\"],",
    "    \"risk_level\": \"safe\",",
    "    \"enabled\": true",
    "  }",
    "",
    "TEMPLATE PACK (groupe de skills) :",
    "  {",
    "    \"id\": \"mon-pack\",",
    "    \"name\": \"Mon Pack\",",
    "    \"description\": \"Description du pack\",",
    "    \"icon\": \"📦\",",
    "    \"skills\": [",
    "      { \"id\": \"skill-a\", \"repo\": \"user/repo\" },",
    "      { \"id\": \"skill-b\", \"repo\": \"user/repo\" }",
    "    ]",
    "  }",
    "",
    "ICÔNES DISPONIBLES (champ 'icon') :",
